---
title: Cumin Chicken and Grilled Carrots with Tahini Dressing and Mint
description: Grilling carrots brings out a smoky sweetness you'll fall in love with! After a drizzle of yogurt-tahini dressing and a sprinkle of mint, they make the perfect side for our juicy cumin-turmeric chicken.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cumin-chicken-and-grilled-carrots-040cb60a.jpg
